<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wilhelm II., Markgraf von Meißen</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Freilassung des gefangenen Christian Haller, Sohn des Peter Haller, Bürger und Ratsherr zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_25" id="11v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_25_r1l13">Marggraf VVilhelm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_25_r1l14">von Meichſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_25_r1l15">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Vns iſt fürkomen . vvie daʒ Criſtan haller des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_25_r1l17">Peter Hallers vnſers <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> burgers 
<add><ab facs="#facs_25_r1l16">vnd Ratgeſellen </ab></add> Sun ſwerlich in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> vngnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_25_r1l18">gefallen vnd darümb mit <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> leib vnd gute cʒugefenknüſſe <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_25_r1l19">vnd noch gen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdıkeit behafft ſeẏ . Bitten vvir ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_25_r1l20">fürſtenlich gnade dinſtlich mit gancʒem fleiſſe . daʒ Jr durch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_25_r1l21"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> vvilligen dinſte willen dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Burgers ſun / ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_25_r1l23">gnade darynne miltiklich beweiſen wöllet / vnd Jn <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_25_r1l24">von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdikeit kumen laſſen . Alſo . daʒ Er vnſer bete </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_25_r1l27">darynne gen 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_25_r1l26"><expan>furſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab></add> gnaden genẏſſe / Als vvir des <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_25_r1l28"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden wol getrawen . das wöllen vvir v̈mb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_25_r1l30">vvilliklich vnd <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> verdienen / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iij̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex>ıs</expan> <expan>Bap<ex>tis</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_25" id="11v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Marggraf Wilhelm von Meichsen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns ist fürkomen
                                                wie daz Cristan Haller, des Peter Hallers unsers
                                                  <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> burgers <add>und
                                                  ratgesellen</add> sun, swerlich in
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> ungnade gefallen und
                                                darümb mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> leib und
                                                gute czu gefenknüsse <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
                                                und noch gen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                                                hochwirdikeit behafft sey. Bitten wir ewr
                                                fürstenlich gnade dinstlich mit ganczem fleisse, daz
                                                ir durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> willigen
                                                dinste willen dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers sun ewr gnade
                                                darynne miltiklich beweisen wöllet und in
                                                  <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdikeit kumen
                                                lassen, also daz er unser bete darynne gen
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<add><expan>furstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan></add>
                                                gnaden genysse, als wir des
                                                  <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden wol getrawen.
                                                Das wöllen wir ümb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> williklich und
                                                  <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> verdienen.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii
                                                  <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex>is</expan>
<expan>bap<ex>tis</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
